summary: I know I’m not the best at drawing, and I couldn’t get the webs on Spidey’s suit to look right, so I just took them out and...
body:
I know I’m not the best at drawing, and I couldn’t get the webs on Spidey’s suit to look right, so I just took them out and tried to get the color patches rightish. I don’t know a lot about Spider-Man haha.

But ever since @mrcamillaa made that post about finger guns in the game, I thought of them doing finger guns at each other and it just kinda spiraled…lol.

@therealjacksepticeye
